Why?

These apps need high CPU / memory

Normal apps should not run there


Taint and tolerants 
-----------------------
Taints and tolerations are used to reserve specific nodes for specific workloads and prevent unwanted pods from running on them.

Taints are applied on nodes to repel pods, and tolerations are applied on pods to allow them to be scheduled on tainted nodes. This helps reserve nodes for specific workloads.


